{"tid":909210,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"芝加哥升降機斷纜急墜84層　6人獲救奇蹟無恙","createTime":"2018-11-20T08:05:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-20T21:15:01.000Z","uid":75969,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5b0935d2a2b01d584689605fc06b117dee25c6dc","tid":909210,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T08:05:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20181120/s00005/de5d18b4a82104589b43ae82cef70aad.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20181120%2Fs00005%2Fde5d18b4a82104589b43ae82cef70aad.jpg&h=106f4cf4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20181120/s00005/dcc94badb4b4021df2f543ac3e6cf378.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20181120%2Fs00005%2Fdcc94badb4b4021df2f543ac3e6cf378.jpg&h=947c3b6e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國芝加哥第4高的摩天大廈「約翰漢考克中心（John Hancock Centre）」，上周五（16日）發生升降機電纜斷裂意外，一部載有包括孕婦在內6人的升降機在95樓突然急墜至11樓。消防員最終花2小時，鑿穿混凝土牆及打開升降機門，救出被困者，事件中沒有人受傷。<br />\n<br />\n事發前，一對墨西哥夫婦遊客、一名孕婦等6人在95層高的餐廳離開，乘搭特快升降機直達地層，其間升降機突然急墜。墨西哥遊客蒙特馬約爾（Jaime Montemayor）說，進入升降機後聽到「卡、卡、卡、」異響，感受到升降機不停下墜，他和太太都以為自己必死無疑。<br />\n<br />\n當時蒙特馬約爾的朋友乘搭另一升降機，並在等待20分鐘後感到不妥。消防員到場後花費2小時，在11樓的車庫鑿穿混凝土牆，打開升降機門救出眾人，當時該升降機已有兩條電纜斷開，搖搖欲墜。<br />\n<br />\n芝加哥消防部門表示，當時形勢危險，升降機上方的電纜斷開，他們必須打破11樓車庫的一面牆，才能打開升降機門。<br />\n<br />\n（天空新聞網）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20181120/s00005/1542693258800\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20181120%2Fs00005%2F1542693258800&d=Q2fpNZjU8e7BPMXOjrwcQRv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=63be718e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20181120%2Fs00005%2F1542693258800&h=231d5b32\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20181120/s00005/1542693258800</a>"},{"pid":"0a511bd66f444e7c3da53f85c3beae5e342165b4","tid":909210,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T08:24:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=2292DtCuiu4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D2292DtCuiu4&d=Q2fpNZjU8e7BPMXOjrwcQRv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=8b8136e6\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=2292DtCuiu4</a>"},{"pid":"235ce51f53fd90680ec1f9d4df602cff260cf9c7","tid":909210,"uid":119401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T21:15:01.000Z","msg":"發過幾次搭升降機惡夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n幾百樓極速跌落地下好恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}